isFinishedAbnormally

boolean isFinishedAbnormally()
Indicates that the process has quit while processing is still not finished. This could happen in the following cases:
  • The process was forced to quit.
  • Processing ended abnormally due to an exception.

    Returns:
    Returns true if processing has stopped abnormally.

    getSuccessesCount

    long getSuccessesCount()
    Gets the count of elements that have been successfully processed. Successful process means that the operation was executed with input the specified elements and it completed without throwing an exception.

    Returns:
